Community.name: xCirrex Media
Community.description: Monthly tournaments in xCirrex's PVP worlds, community hangouts and concerts!

events.name: Working Out w/ Soaring Fitness
events.marketing: Come get a taste of what Soaring Fitness has to offer! Sora and a team of VR fitness instructors will go over the basics of working out in VR, lead some routines that everyone can participate in, and explain how VR can become an integral part of your own personal fitness journey. All skill levels are welcome, and no extra equipment is required.

Community.name: Soaring Fitness
Community.description: We are a VR-based workout group, focused on being freely accessible. Our hard working team of Volunteers offer their time and experience to make it all possible. Our Certified Personal Trainers work with our Volunteer Instructors to bring you workouts 7 days a week! We believe good health and fitness should not be gated behind a paywall!

events.name: Pool Tournament with Pool Parlor
events.marketing: Pool Parlor welcomes everyone to come grab a cue and join in a friendly tournament! 32 players will be playing against one another in hopes to be the winner! The Winner will get their picture in the world, the tournament winner cue, and a discord role! All participants and referees will get a special cue for playing in tournament.

Community.name: Pool Parlor
Community.description: The Pool Parlor is a community striving to make a strong connection with everyone and one of the best pool tables around!

events.name: The Basics and Essentials of Cinematic Storytelling
events.marketing: Wanna learn what it takes to make a film? Well then Gerzybow's got your back! With over 7+ years of video production experience, feel free to hop in as one of the Studio Executives at Portal Media demonstrates tips and tricks to telling your story in the most visually compelling ways possible!

Community.name: The Synapse
Community.description: We are a fun-loving community focusing on weekly VR games and events. Along with games and events, we emphasize art and media creation, support for artists, manga development, and community fundraising and charities. The Synapse aims to be the community guides of VRChat, providing an amazing and friendly place for people to hangout and be themselves.

events.name: Kocho no Boss Rush
events.marketing: "Kochō no Boss Rush" is an immersive roleplay event organized by the community Kochō no Yakuza. The event aims to engage and train the public in the art of fighting and roleplaying, specifically centered around epic boss encounters they usually have within the community. It offers participants a unique opportunity to learn combat techniques, enhance their roleplaying skills, and then put their newly acquired abilities to the test in a thrilling boss scenario.

Community.name: Kochō no Yakuza
Community.description: Kochō no Yakuza is a VRChat roleplay community themed after the Yakuza game series and Japanese culture in general. The group was founded on 1st of September 2021 by Ginger Tea. They wish to provide, bring together and entertain. Providing a friendlier place for VRChat public to roleplay in is one of the aims they wish to achieve, alongside with helping other communities with bigger projects. Bringing together both new and veteran players who have nowhere else to go, educating people about VRChat as a whole and keeping them up to date on what is going on in this vast but confusing place. Entertaining both the public and their people with external and internal roleplay which are still in development. Giving people a place to feel welcomed and a place anybody can feel they belong to.
